# Phase 1: AI Insights as a Native AAP Feature

## Core Concept: "AI-Assisted Job Analysis"

### Simple UX:

```
Job Template Settings
├── General
├── Details
├── Execution Environment
└── [NEW] ✅ Enable AI Insights
    ├── AI Endpoint URL: [https://customer-ai.example.com/v1/chat/completions]
    ├── API Token: [•••••••]
    ├── Model: [granite-3.1-8b-instruct] (optional)
    └── Integration:
        ○ AAP Only (show insights in job output)
        ○ ServiceNow (create/update incidents with AI insights)
        ○ Email (include in failure notifications)
```

